{"lemma":"فَرْطُ","slug":"فَرْطُ","root":"ف.ر.ط","root_slug":"ف-ر-ط","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ر-ط","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"فَرْطُ","root":"فرط","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":7,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":12},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n33589","n33594","n33595","n33596","n33597"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%B7%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to precede, to pass, to outgo, to slip, to shed, to strip","tags":["ambitransitive"],"examples":[{"text":"قَالَا رَبَّنَا إِنَّنَا نَخَافُ أَن يَفْرُطَ عَلَيْنَا أَوْ أَن يَطْغَىٰ","english":"They said: Our Lord, indeed we fear that they hasten against us or transgress!"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to send before; to hand over, to make go before"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to forgo, to abandon, to let slide, to slight, to relinquish, to let go away, to dump","examples":[{"text":"ينبغي أن نكون صارميم والا انتهينا, إن قوتنا تكمن في مواقفنا الشجاعة التي لايمكن أن نفرط بها.","english":"The vital thing is that we stay rugged and have not quitted. For our power hides in our dauntless positions which to relinquish is unworkable for us."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to dissipate, to squander, to splurge"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of فَرَطَ (faraṭa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"excess, exorbitance, over-","examples":[{"text":"فَرْطُ ٱلتَّعَرُّقِ","english":"hyperhidrosis"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"erect waymark, sign set up to show the right way"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"one who goes forth, or precedes, preceder, foregoer"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"reward, recompense prepared beforehand"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"swift horse"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a case or affair in which the due limits are exceeded","examples":[{"text":"وَلَا تُطِعْ مَنْ أَغْفَلْنَا قَلْبَهُ عَن ذِكْرِنَا وَاتَّبَعَ هَوَاهُ وَكَانَ أَمْرُهُ فُرُطًا","english":"And do not obey whose heart we have made heedless of our remembrance and who follows his lust and whose affair is in excess of limits!"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a hill or eminence resembling a mountain"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n33589","headword_ar":"فَرَطَ","root":"frT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"furuwTN","text_ar":"فُرُوطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"preceded; went before; was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, before, beforehand, first,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foremost; had,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"got, priority,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"precedence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariTa","text_ar":"فَرِطَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", [inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTN","text_ar":"فَرَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; which is therefore used as an epithet applied to one and to more;] (O, TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AftrT","text_ar":"افترط","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AftrT A_ilayohi","text_ar":"افترط اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY h`*aA AlA^amori","text_ar":"فِى هٰذَا الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was foremost in attaining to him in this affair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mufotariTN","text_ar":"مُفْتَرِطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTa","text_ar":"فَرَطَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqawoma","text_ar":"القَوْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb, K, &c.,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faroTN","text_ar":"فَرْطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"furuwTN","text_ar":"فُرُوطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) or both, (O,) or the former and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraATapN","text_ar":"فَرَاطَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He preceded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went before, the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"company of men,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, O, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in search of water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to come to water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the purpose of preparing the buckets and ropes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the purpose of putting into a right state the watering-trough"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and ropes"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, O)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and buckets,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, O, K,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to prepare these for them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See also 5.] ―         -b3-  An Arab of the desert said to El-Hasan,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eal~imoniY diynFA","text_ar":"عَلِّمْنِى دِينًا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wasuwTFA laA *aAhibFA furuwTFA walaA saAqiTFA suquwTFA","text_ar":"وَسُوطًا لَا ذَاهِبًا فُرُوطًا وَلَا سَاقِطًا سُقُوطًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Teach thou me a religion of the middle sort, not passing beyond the due mean, nor falling short of it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTa minohu","text_ar":"فَرَطَ مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It proceeded from him hastily, before reflection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without premeditation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as thought it preceded his judgment;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badara","text_ar":"بَدَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqa","text_ar":"سَبَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqad~ama","text_ar":"تَقَدَّمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See 3.] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTa minohu kalaAmN","text_ar":"فَرَطَ مِنْهُ كَلَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Speech proceeded from him hastily, before reflection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without premeditation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqa","text_ar":"سَبَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqad~ama","text_ar":"تَقَدَّمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTa","text_ar":"فَرَطَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilayohi min~iY qawolN","text_ar":"اـِلَيْهِ مِنِّى قَوْلٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A saying proceeded to him from me hastily, before reflection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without premeditation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqa","text_ar":"سَبَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) And in like manner you say of an evil action. (TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTa Ealayohi","text_ar":"فَرَطَ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hasted to do him an evil action:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he acted hastily and unjustly towards him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2376},{"kind":"text","text":"TA.) Hence, in the Kur [xx. 47],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~aA naxaAfu A^ano","text_ar":"اـِنَّا نَخَافُ اَنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaforuTa EalayonaA","text_ar":"يَفْرُطَ عَلَيْنَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily we fear that he may act hastily and unjustly towards us:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that he may hastily do to us an evil action:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Arafeh, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that he may hasten to punish us."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, Bd, O, Jel.) [See also 4.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTa Ealayohi","text_ar":"فَرَطَ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did to him what was disagreeable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hateful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil; he annoyed him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTa","text_ar":"فَرَطَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"furuwTN","text_ar":"فُرُوطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He reviled."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IKtt.) You say also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTa Ealayohi fiY","text_ar":"فَرَطَ عَلَيْهِ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqawoli","text_ar":"القَوْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 4, latter half. ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTa fiyhi","text_ar":"فَرَطَ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 2, near the middle. ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTa fiY HawoDihi","text_ar":"فَرَطَ فِى حَوْضِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 4, last sentence but one. ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTati Aln~axolapu","text_ar":"فَرَطَتِ النَّخْلَةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The palm-tree was left without being fecundated until its spadix became dry and hard"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EasaA","text_ar":"عَسَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea$A","text_ar":"عَشا"},{"kind":"text","text":", and in the O"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaEosuw","text_ar":"يَعْسُو"},{"kind":"text","text":"). (O, K, * TA.) ―         -b9-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTati","text_ar":"فَرَطَتِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albiy^oru","text_ar":"البِيْرُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The well was left until its water had collected again."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTa A_ilayohi rasuwlahu","text_ar":"فَرَطَ اـِلَيْهِ رَسُولَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 2. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTa wulodFA","text_ar":"فَرَطَ وُلْدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waladFA","text_ar":"وَلَدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTa waladahu","text_ar":"فَرَطَ وَلَدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 4."}],"source_refs":["O","K","TA","S","Msb","M"]},{"entry_id":"n33594","headword_ar":"فَرْطٌ","root":"frT","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Excess; extravagance; exorbitance; an exceeding degree; an exceeding of the due bounds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"just limits."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, * TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iy~aAka","text_ar":"اـِيَّاكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAlfaroTa fiY AlA^amori","text_ar":"وَالفَرْطَ فِى الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Avoid thou,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beware thou of, excess in the affair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mastery, ascendency, prevalence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"predominance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) as, for instance, of eager desire, and of grief. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A time, whether long or short; an indefinite time;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiynN","text_ar":"حِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laqiytuhu fiY AlfaroTi baEoda AlfaroTi","text_ar":"لَقِيتُهُ فِى الفَرْطِ بَعْدَ الفَرْطِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I met him time after time."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anaA A=tiyhi AlfaroTa","text_ar":"اَنَا ا=تِيهِ الفَرْطَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I come to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"will come to him, at some time."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  It also denotes one's meeting a man, (TA,) or coming to him, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after some days,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) accord. to A 'Obeyd; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not more than fifteen days,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"than fifteen nights,"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to the same, (S, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nor less than three."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anaA A^aloqaAhu fiY AlfaroTi","text_ar":"اَنَا اَلْقَاهُ فِى الفَرْطِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I meet him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"will meet him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shall meet him, after some days"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) [But the above-mentioned restriction does not apply when it is prefixed to a noun signifying a period of time: for] you say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atayotuhu faroTa yawomK A^awo yawomayoni","text_ar":"اَتَيْتُهُ فَرْطَ يَوْمٍ اَوْ يَوْمَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I came to him after a day or two days"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O.) [It is said in the TA that, accord. to ISk, it is used in the saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=tiyka faroTa yawomK A^awo","text_ar":"ا=تِيكَ فَرْطَ يَوْمٍ اَوْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomayoni","text_ar":"يَوْمَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and that it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a day between two days;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but this seems to me to be a mistake for"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between a day and two days:"},{"kind":"text","text":"it is afterwards said in the TA that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faroTa yawomK A^awo yawomayoni","text_ar":"فَرْطَ يَوْمٍ اَوْ يَوْمَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after two days;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but the complete explanation should doubtless be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after a day or two days."},{"kind":"text","text":"] Lebeed says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"hali Aln~afosu A_il~aA mutoEapN musotaEaArapN\n                      \n                     \n                        tuEaAru fataA^otiY rab~ahaA faroTa A^a$ohuri"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Is the soul aught but a borrowed thing to be enjoyed, which is lent, and goes to its Lord after some months?"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) And an Arab said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDayotu","text_ar":"مَضَيْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faroTa saAEapK walamo A^uwmino A^ano A^anofalita","text_ar":"فَرْطَ سَاعَةٍ وَلَمْ اُومِنْ اَنْ اَنْفَلِتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and being asked “ What is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"frT sAEp","text_ar":"فرط ساعة"},{"kind":"text","text":"? ” he answered, “ Like since thou begannest to speak: ” he meant ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I went away after a little while,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a little while ago, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"] by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lm","text_ar":"لم"},{"kind":"text","text":"and what follows it,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I did not feel sure of my escaping."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small mountain;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) pl., accord. to Kr,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"furuTN","text_ar":"فُرُطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: (TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"head of an"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eminence such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akamap","text_ar":"اَكَمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  And the same, (K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTN","text_ar":"فَرَطٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (thus as written in the O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An erect way-mark,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing set up for guidance to the right way:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aforuTN","text_ar":"اَفْرُطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aforaATN","text_ar":"اَفْرَاطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) [but] it is said in the A that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badato","text_ar":"بَدَتْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lanaA A^aforaATu AlmafaAzapi","text_ar":"لَنَا اَفْرَاطُ المَفَازَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a tropical saying, signifying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA","text_ar":"مَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@sotaqodama mino A^aEolaAmihaA","text_ar":"ا@سْتَقْدَمَ مِنْ اَعْلَامِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as though meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The foremost of the way-marks of the desert,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waterless desert, appeared to us"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","S","O"]},{"entry_id":"n33595","headword_ar":"فُرْطٌ","root":"frT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"furuTN","text_ar":"فُرُطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", near the end."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n33596","headword_ar":"فَرَطٌ","root":"frT","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A person who goes before,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in advance of, others, to the water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who is sent before,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in advance, to seek water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and who prepares for them the ropes and buckets,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and plasters with mud"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in one copy of the S"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and fills"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the watering-troughs, and draws water for them;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAriTN","text_ar":"فَارِطٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Mgh, O, Msb, TA;) being of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEalN","text_ar":"فَعَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAEilN","text_ar":"فَاعِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, TA,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tabaEN","text_ar":"تَبَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taAbiEN","text_ar":"تَابِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a number of persons who perform that office;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fur~aATN","text_ar":"فُرَّاطٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K, TA,) pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAriTN","text_ar":"فَارِطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb, TA:) you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN faraTN","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ فَرَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawomN faraTN","text_ar":"قَوْمٌ فَرَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anaA","text_ar":"اَنَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTukumo EalaY AlHawoDi","text_ar":"فَرَطُكُمْ عَلَى الحَوْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I"},{"kind":"text","text":"shall be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"your preceder to the pool of Paradise"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAriTN","text_ar":"فَارِطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  [Hence,] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A child"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that dies"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not having attained to puberty:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) [whence the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AifotaraTa faraTFA","text_ar":"اِفْتَرَطَ فَرَطًا"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 4:] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aforaATN","text_ar":"اَفْرَاطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTN","text_ar":"فَرَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is both sing. and pl. [in this sense]. (TA.) ―         -b4-  Hence also, (S, Msb,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A reward,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"recompense, prepared in advance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beforehand:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a work,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an action, of the same kind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) You say, of an infant that has died, (S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aall~`hum~a A@joEalohu lanaA faraTFA","text_ar":"اَللّٰهُمَّ ا@جْعَلْهُ لَنَا فَرَطًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O God, make him to be a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cause of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reward,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"recompense, prepared in advance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beforehand, for us."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb.) ―         -b5-  [Hence also,] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Water"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at which one arrives"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in advance of other waters."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b6-  [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aforaATu AlS~uboHi","text_ar":"اَفْرَاطُ الصُّبْحِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~abaAHi","text_ar":"الصَّبَاحِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The annunciations,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foretokens,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the beginnings of the annunciations"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foretokens,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the daybreak:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) sing."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTN","text_ar":"فَرَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Lth, TA.) ―         -b7-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faroTN","text_ar":"فَرْطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence.       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Haste."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  See also the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","K","Msb","O","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n33597","headword_ar":"فُرُطٌ","root":"frT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"swift"},{"kind":"text","text":"horse; (S, O, K;) one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that precedes, outgoes, outstrips,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gets before, others:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, O:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aforaATN","text_ar":"اَفْرَاطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L, TA.) ―         -b2-  A case, or an affair,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which the due bounds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"just limits, are exceeded:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"neglected;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTN","text_ar":"فَرَطٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"despised and neglected."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHeyth, O, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kul~u A^amori fulaAnK furuTN","text_ar":"كُلُّ اَمْرِ فُلَانٍ فُرُطٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The whole of the case of such a person is one in which the due bounds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"just limits, are exceeded."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) And it is said in the Kur [xviii. 27],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wakaAna","text_ar":"وَكَانَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amoruhu furuTFA","text_ar":"اَمْرُهُ فُرُطًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And whose case is one in which the due bounds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"just limits, are exceeded:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which obedience is neglected and unheeded:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"preference of backwardness"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqodiymu AlEajozi","text_ar":"تَقْدِيمُ العَجْزِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (Zj:) or ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"repentance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to some, the meaning is that which here next follows: (O, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wrongdoing; injustice; transgression:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA:) some say also, that it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hastening,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acceleration."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"furuTN","text_ar":"فُرُطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"furoTN","text_ar":"فُرْطٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eminence such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akamap","text_ar":"اَكَمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling a mountain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) or the second, accord. to Zbd, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"base"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safoH","text_ar":"سَفْح"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a mountain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aforaATN","text_ar":"اَفْرَاطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zbd, S, O) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aforuTN","text_ar":"اَفْرُطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faroTN","text_ar":"فَرْطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence but one.]"}],"source_refs":["S","A","O","K","TA","Zj","Zbd"]}]}}